#summary RainbowDashboard includes eight built-in images displayed using the SHOW_IMAGE and DRAW_IMAGE commands.

RainbowDashboard includes eight built-in images displayed using the `SHOW_IMAGE` and `DRAW_IMAGE` commands, the first five of which are identical to the built-in images provided by the standard firmware. They are shown here for reference. Image number 6 is particularly useful when determining desired gamma levels to be set with the `SET_GAMMA` command.
